Purview Posture Analyzer
========================

This project is a modernized, read-only Microsoft Purview posture analyzer.

It is derived in part from the MIT-licensed project:

    Configuration Analyzer for Microsoft Purview (CAMP)
    https://github.com/OfficeDev/CAMP
    Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation.

The original CAMP MIT license is preserved in the LICENSE file.

Portions of the architecture (the dynamic file-convention loader pattern and the
per-area cmdlet inventory used by collectors) are inspired by CAMP. The collection,
analysis, and reporting logic has been rewritten.

IMPORTANT
